The death of the Russian scientist adds to the list of people engaged in coronavirus research dropping dead in mysterious circumstances.
List of Assassinations of COVID-19 Researchers
1. Canadian Scientist Frank Plummer
2. Professor Bing Liu, University of Pittsburgh
3. Gita Ramjee, an HIV scientist
4. WHO driver carrying Coronavirus samples shot dead
5. Vaccine Whistleblower Brandy Vaughan
